data.title: 2023-24 College Team Academic Award Winners Announced
data.text:
KANSAS CITY, Mo. (August 1, 2024) – United Soccer Coaches announced on Thursday the College Team Academic Award winners, recognized for their exemplary performance in the classroom during the 2023-24 academic year.

A total of 461 soccer teams (189 men, 272 women) posted a team grade point average of 3.0 or higher, thereby earning the United Soccer Coaches Team Academic Award for the 2023-24 academic year. Of that total, 113 schools had both their men’s and women’s programs recognized
